            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1600783769380-december-2020--exploring-neurodiversity-in-employment" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#809d09e2-0338-4245-98ab-ee356bf92c5f" href="#accordion-content-1600783769380-december-2020--exploring-neurodiversity-in-employment" aria-controls="accordion-content-1600783769380-december-2020--exploring-neurodiversity-in-employment" aria-expanded="false">
                            December 2020: Exploring Neurodiversity in Employment
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1600783769380-december-2020--exploring-neurodiversity-in-employment" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1600783769380-december-2020--exploring-neurodiversity-in-employment">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1600783769380 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="a9aa53b9-34b2-4a71-a826-1c56be8fb5da" >

    <p><strong>Date:</strong> December 8, 2020</p> 
<p><strong>Time:</strong> 12:00 p.m. - 1:30 p.m.</p> 
<p><strong>Location:</strong> Zoom</p> 
<p><strong>Cost:</strong> FREE</p> 
<p><strong><a href="http://bit.ly/InvestinginInclusion-neurodiversity  " target="_blank">Register for Exploring Neurodiversity in Employment<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a></strong></p> 
<p><img src="/etc.clientlibs/ryecms/static/clientlib-site/resources/images/separators/transparent_separator.png" alt=" " role="presentation" class="hr-separator hr-separator-default">We are partnering with the <a href="http://www.casda.ca/">Canadian Autism Spectrum Disorder Alliance (CASDA)<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a> to explore an often untapped human resource: Neurodiverse Candidates.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>It is well known that diversifying your employee identity profile has a direct positive impact on your business's bottom line. Hiring neurodiverse candidates impacts your bottom line and offers many other benefits. Whether it is innovation, productivity, or diversity of thought, these candidates add so much to a business but are often overlooked.&nbsp;</p> 
<p>This webinar will feature businesses who have leveraged the potential of Neurodiverse candidates and share how they did it, what they gained from it, and how you can do it too.</p> 
<p>Join us for an informative and invigorating discussion about hiring and working with Neurodiverse candidates.</p>
    





</div>
