<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="e9301f4b-7284-4eb7-b593-141f24207211" >

    <p>With diversity and inclusion as a core tenant at Ryerson, helping to create inclusive work spaces ensures that our students are entering careers they can thrive in. Our offerings are a way for our employer partners to begin a conversation or to support you and your teams to progress further in your knowledge of recruiting and retaining diverse talent.</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Our suite of training sessions are highlighted here.</li> 
 <li>Sessions can be delivered onsite or at Ryerson.</li> 
